<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 8 kohaldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Application of &sect; 8 of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist tekkinud puhkusen&otilde;udele ei kohaldata aegumist. </eesti>
<inglise>Limitation period does not apply to claims for entitlement to holiday which arise before the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
