<eesti>Avaliku teenistuse seaduse (RT I 1995, 16, 228; 1999, 7, 112; 10, 155; 16, 271 ja 276; 2000, 25, 144 ja 145; 28, 167; 102, 672; 2001, 7, 17 ja 18; 17, 78) &sect; 133 l&otilde;ikes 2 asendatakse s&otilde;na "naist" s&otilde;naga "isikut". </eesti>
<inglise>In subsection 133 (2) of the Public Service Act (RT I 1995, 16, 228; 1999, 7, 112; 10, 155; 16, 271 and 276; 2000, 25, 144 and 145; 28, 167; 102, 672; 2001, 7, 17 and 18; 17, 78), the word "woman" is substituted by the word "person". </inglise>
